REALTOR, Certified Military Residential Specialist ,Certified Short Sale Professional Expert

Buying or selling a home? Whether it is your first home or second home, it is very exciting but can also be very stressful. For most people, this will be the largest transaction financially in their life and I am here to make the process go smoothly. I have been a business owner since 1987 with my husband and know that being a good negotiator on behalf of my clients is one of the most important things. With this, I am knowledgeable of how best to negotiate on your behalf for the purchase and or sale of your home. Since my clients put their trust in me, I have an obligation to ensure the process is done right. Search for homes that fit your needs at www.teamweiser.com. It's easy to ask questions or schedule a visit from our site also. This is a great way to get your home search started, but having an experienced agent showing you homes and following through with the paperwork process will allow the transaction to move to a smooth closing. My goal is to find you the right home so you are 100% satisfied with the service and your new home and you tell your friends and family members. I look forward to working with you in the near future.
